'''Nagaian''' was the native language of the [[Nagai/Legends|Nagai]] species from [[Nagi/Legends|Nagi]]. It was a language characterized by slight variations of tone and pitch, resulting in what some regarded as a musical, lilting quality.<ref name="LECG">''[[Legacy Era Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

Most Nagai were fluent in both Nagaian and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="UAA">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref> While other species were capable of learning the language, few were able to master it.<ref name="LECG" />

